Rooms.Name: A Light Forest Trailhead
Rooms.Description: You stand at the trailhead of the vast forest, the clearing a bustling hub of activity. The ground is firm beneath your feet, packed hard from the countless footsteps of travelers who have passed this way. A wooden signpost rises from the earth, pointing the way ahead and marking the fork in the trail that splits off to the east towards the majestic city of Astoria. The towering walls and palisades of Astoria are visible on the horizon, their imposing height and the glint of steel from the West Gate lending an air of power and security to the city.

Rooms.Name: A Trail Through the Light Forest
Rooms.Description: You are traversing a winding path through the dense forest, with the trees towering overhead, filtering dappled light onto the forest floor. To your east, the trees begin to thin and you can see glimpses of the lush grasslands beyond, while to the west, the trail continues its winding journey deeper into the heart of the forest.

Rooms.Name: A Trail Through the Light Forest

Rooms.Name: A small path in the dense forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a small path leading through the dense forest.  The crowns of the
old trees leave the forest in an unreal twilight illumination.  The path
continues north and south.

Rooms.Name: A small path in the dense forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a small path leading through the dense forest.  The crowns of the
old trees leave the forest in an unreal twilight illumination.  The path
continues north and east.

Rooms.Name: An intersection in the dense forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a small path leading through the dense forest.  The crowns of the
old trees leave the forest in an unreal twilight illumination.  The forest
gradually lightens to the east.  Paths lead east, west and south.

Rooms.Name: The forest clearing
Rooms.Description:
You are in a clearing in the forest.  Lots of fresh stumps of varying sizes
protrude from the ground and heavy logs are stacked neatly in a big pile
supported by stakes set into the ground.  Paths lead north, east and west.

Rooms.Name: Outside a small cabin in the forest
Rooms.Description:
You are outside a small cabin built entirely from heavy logs.  There is a
wooden door to the north and small paths lead west and south through the trees.

Rooms.Name: Inside the cabin
Rooms.Description:
You are inside a small one-room cabin made entirely from heavy logs.  It is
very sparsely furnished, containing only most basic housekeeping equipment,
such as a bed, a chair and a table.

Rooms.Name: A small path through the light forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a small path leading through the forest.  The trees are tall and
slender.  Paths lead north and south.

Rooms.Name: An intersection in the dense forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a small path leading through the dense forest.  The crowns of the
old trees leave the forest floor in an unreal twilight illumination.  Paths
lead north, east and south.

Rooms.Name: A small path in the dense forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a small path leading through the dense forest.  The crowns of the
old trees leave the forest in an unreal twilight illumination.  The path
continues east and west.

Rooms.Name: An intersection in the dense forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a small path leading through the dense forest.  The forest gradually
lightens to the north.  Paths lead north, east and west.

Rooms.Name: A small path in the dense forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a small path leading through the dense forest.  The crowns of the
old trees leave the forest in an unreal twilight illumination.  The path
continues south and west.

Rooms.Name: A small path in the dense forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a small path leading through the dense forest.  The crowns of the
old trees leave the forest in an unreal twilight illumination.  The path
continues north and south.

Rooms.Name: A small path in the dense forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a small path leading through the dense forest.  The forest seems to
become lighter to the west.  The path continues north and west.

Rooms.Name: An intersection in the light forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a small path leading through the forest.  A path leads north to a
small field and other paths lead east and west into the dense forest.

Rooms.Name: A small path in the dense forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a small path leading through the dense forest.  The forest seems to
become lighter to the east.  The path continues north and east.

Rooms.Name: A small path in the dense forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a small path leading through the dense forest.  The crowns of the
old trees leave the forest in an unreal twilight illumination.  The path
continues south and west.

Rooms.Name: A small path in the dense forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a small path leading through the dense forest.  To the west there is
a cave entrance.  The path continues north and east.

Rooms.Name: Inside the cave
Rooms.Description:
You are in a natural cave.  Various sorts of debris cover the stone floor,
emitting a rather unpleasant smell that makes the air thick and hard to
breathe.  The only obvious exit is east.

Rooms.Name: On a small, grassy field
Rooms.Description:
You are in a small, grassy field somewhere in the forest.  The tall grass
nearly reaches your waist, and the surrounding oaks and beeches form an almost
wall-like thicket on all sides of the field.  A small path leads south through
the trees.

Rooms.Name: A narrow trail through the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a narrow trail winding its way between the enormous, grey trunks.
The crowns of the trees must be very dense, as they leave the forest floor in
utter darkness.  The trail leads east and west.

Rooms.Name: A narrow trail through the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a dusty trail winding its way east-west between huge, ancient trees
whose grey trunks remind you of ancient pillars in a enormous, deserted hall.
To the south, a frail path leads away from the trail.

Rooms.Name: A narrow trail through the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a dusty trail winding its way east-west between huge, ancient trees
that stand close on all sides.  Not a sound is to be heard - everything is
ominously quiet.

Rooms.Name: A narrow trail through the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are where the dusty trail bends, as to avoid conflict with a colossal
trunk to the west.  Not a sound is to be heard - everything is ominously quiet.
The trail leads east and south.

Rooms.Name: A small path in the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a narrow path leading through the deep, dark forest.  You feel as if
the ancient trees observe you in watchful silence.  The path continues north
and south.

Rooms.Name: A small path in the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a narrow path leading through the deep, dark forest.  Ancient grey
trees loom all around you.  The path continues north and west.

Rooms.Name: A junction in the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are by a junction where three paths meet.  Ancient grey trees tower above
you on all sides.  Paths lead east, south and west.

Rooms.Name: A small path in the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a narrow path leading through the deep, dark forest.  Ancient grey
trees loom all around you.  The path continues north and east.

Rooms.Name: A narrow trail through the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a dusty trail winding its way between huge, ancient trees
standing close on all sides.  The trail leads north and west and to the south,
a frail path leads away from the trail.

Rooms.Name: A narrow trail through the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a dusty trail winding its way east-west between huge, ancient trees
that stand close on all sides.  Not a sound is to be heard - everything is
ominously quiet.

Rooms.Name: A narrow trail through the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a dusty trail winding its way between huge, ancient trees that stand
close on all sides.  The trail leads east and south.  To the north, a narrow
path leads away from the trail.

Rooms.Name: A narrow trail through the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a dusty trail winding its way north-south between huge, ancient
trees that loom ominously above you.

Rooms.Name: A narrow trail through the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a dusty trail winding its way between huge, ancient trees
standing close on all sides.  The trail leads north and west and to the east,
a frail path leads away from the trail.

Rooms.Name: A small path in the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a narrow path leading through the deep, dark forest.  Ancient grey
trees loom in all directions.  The path continues south and west.

Rooms.Name: A junction in the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are by a junction where three paths meet.  Ancient grey trees tower above
you on all sides.  Paths lead north, east and west.

Rooms.Name: A small path in the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a narrow path leading through the deep, dark forest.  You feel as
if the ancient trees observe you in watchful silence.  The path continues north
and west.

Rooms.Name: A small path in the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a narrow path leading through the deep, dark forest.  Giant, grey
trees loom ominously on all sides.  The path continues east and south.

Rooms.Name: A junction in the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are by a junction where three paths meet.  Ancient, grey trees seem to
observe you silently you from all sides.  Paths lead north, east and west.

Rooms.Name: A small path in the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a narrow path leading through the deep, dark forest.  Ancient,
grey trees loom everywhere.  The path continues south and west.

Rooms.Name: A small path in the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a narrow path leading through the deep, dark forest.  Huge, ancient
trees are on all sides.  The path continues north and south.

Rooms.Name: On the river bank in the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a narrow path leading through the deep, dark forest.  To the south a
fast river is flowing westwards through the forest.  Ancient grey trees loom on
both banks.  The path continues north and west.

Rooms.Name: Beginning of a bridge across the dark river
Rooms.Description:
The path widens and becomes a trail or maybe even a road with as
packed as it is. It seems well maintained and like it may receive heavy use.
Trees still line the banks and block travel north and west. The river is not very fast here, and a lot of
logs under the bridge seem to be slowing the flow even more.
The river banks are covered with medium rocks, and the bed of the river looks like
small pebbles worn smooth from the river through the passage of time.

Rooms.Name: A small path in the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a narrow path leading through the deep, dark forest.  Giant, grey
trees loom ominously all around.  The path continues east and south.

Rooms.Name: A junction on the river bank in the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are by a junction where three paths meet.  Ancient, grey trees seem to
observe you silently you from all around.  To the south a dark river flows from
east to west through the forest.  Paths lead north, east and west.

Rooms.Name: A dead end path in the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a narrow path leading through the deep, dark forest.  The ancient
trees stand so close that the path disappears between the dusty roots.  To the
south a dark river flows from east to west.  The only exit appears to be west.

Rooms.Name: A small path on the river bank in the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a narrow path leading through the deep, dark forest.  Ancient grey
trees loom everywhere.  To the south you smell marsh gas.  The path continues
north and east.

Rooms.Name: A narrow trail through the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a dusty trail winding its way between huge, ancient trees standing
close on all sides.  The trail leads north and west, and to the south a frail
path leads away from the trail.

Rooms.Name: A narrow trail through the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a dusty trail winding its way between huge, ancient trees
standing close on all sides.  The trail leads east and south.

Rooms.Name: A narrow trail through the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a dusty trail winding its way east-west between huge, ancient trees
that stand close on all sides.  Not a sound is to be heard - everything is
ominously quiet.

Rooms.Name: A narrow trail through the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a dusty trail winding its way east-west between huge, ancient trees
that stand close on all sides.  Not a sound is to be heard - everything is
ominously quiet.

Rooms.Name: A narrow trail through the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a dusty trail winding its way westwards just below huge sticky
wires suspended like ropes between the trees.  To the west the path seems to
be completely covered in a giant web made from huge threads covered with glue.
This place gives you the creeps.

Rooms.Name: The spider web
Rooms.Description:
You are walking along the narrow path, ducking under the sticky ropes as you
advance...
>
A huge, poisonous spider drops from above!
A huge, poisonous spider drops from above!
A huge, poisonous spider drops from above!
>
The huge, poisonous spider stings you!  You resist the poison!
The huge, poisonous spider stings you!  You are poisoned!
The huge, poisonous spider stings you!  You are poisoned!
>
You've fallen, and you can't get up!!!!!

Rooms.Name: Up in the tree
Rooms.Description:
You are hanging on the outside of a huge tree trunk covered in a sticky
substance.  Directly to the west is an immense spider web suspended between
numerous of the giant trees including the one you are hanging on.

Rooms.Name: On the spider web
Rooms.Description:
You are balancing carefully on the giant sticky threads that holds the giant
web in place.  To the east is a giant tree trunk and to the west is an entrance
to a cave-like structure made from many layers of spider web.

Rooms.Name: The Den of the Queen Spider
Rooms.Description:
You are inside a cave-like structure that seems to be made entirely from
countless layers of spider web.  Temperature and humidity is very high making
it hard to breathe the foul air that lingers here.  The walls are covered with
open cocoons.

Rooms.Name: A dusty trail in the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a dusty trail leading through the deep, dark forest.  Ancient grey
trees loom all around you.  The trail continues north and east.

Rooms.Name: A dusty trail in the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a dusty trail leading through the deep, dark forest.  Ancient,
grey trees loom everywhere.  The trail continues south and west.  A broad
irregular path leads eastwards away from the trail.

Rooms.Name: At the end of the trail through the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a dusty trail leading through the deep, dark forest.  Ancient grey
trees loom all around you.  You see a dark grove north of you.
The only other exit is east.

Rooms.Name: Outside a cave in the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are at the end of a broad, irregular path.  To the north is a very large
ominous-looking cave opening.  The trees here have many marks as if something
with huge claws has been tearing at them in rage.

Rooms.Name: The cave of the Green Dragon
Rooms.Description:
You are in a big natural cave.  The floor is littered with bones of all sorts
and the stench is so massive that you could cut it with a knife.  The only exit
is to the south.

Rooms.Name: A small path in the deep, dark forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a narrow path leading through the deep, dark forest.  Ancient,
grey trees loom everywhere.  The tree trunks here seem to be covered in some
sticky substance.  The path continues south and west.

Rooms.Name: The narrow trail.
Rooms.Description:
This trail looks much spookier than any other thats you have seen.  The usual
animal claw marks and bites on the trees are getting far and few between. The
trail continues north.

Rooms.Name: The narrow trail.
Rooms.Description:
This area of the trail is also very peculiar.  You can see no signs of animal
life what so ever.  The structure of the surrounding trees forces the path to
make a sharp turn to the east.

Rooms.Name: The circle of trees.
Rooms.Description:
The trees here seem to form a circle around a HUGE tree that is in the center
of them.  You notice a wooden door carved into the huge tree to the east.  The
trail that you followed to get here seems to end at the base of the tree.

Rooms.Name: Inside the great tree.
Rooms.Description:
You have stepped inside of this hollowed tree.  From here steps lead down into
darkness or you can exit the tree by going west.

Rooms.Name: The underground hallway.
Rooms.Description:
This hallway is apparently one of the roots of the tree hollowed out.  The hall
leads south to a room where you hear strange noises or you can go up the steps.

Rooms.Name: The cultist temple.
Rooms.Description:
This temple is built to some god that you don't worship.  It is a nice place
to visit but you feel very uncomfortable about spending much time here.
The wooden altar seems almost to glow as you enter the room.  The only exit is
the way you came in.

Rooms.Name: A trail through the dense forest
Rooms.Description: You find yourself on a narrow path, its twists and turns leading you deeper into the heart of the dense forest. The ancient trees tower high above you, their verdant crowns interlocking to form a natural cathedral of green. Their thick branches cast a dappled light upon the forest floor, bathing the area in an ethereal and otherworldly glow. The path winds its way through the trees, the sound of crunching leaves and twigs beneath your feet the only sign of your progress. To either side, the forest presses in close, its underbrush and brambles lending a sense of mystery and danger to your journey. Ahead of you, the path stretches on, its course marked by the twists and turns of gnarled roots that burst through the earth. It continues east and west, a ribbon of light in an otherwise dark and enchanting world.

Rooms.Name: A trail through the dense forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a small path leading through the dense forest. The crowns of the old
trees leave the forest in an unreal twilight illumination. The path continues
east and south. There seems to be a cave to the north of here.

Rooms.Name: A trail through the dense forest
Rooms.Description:
You are on a small path leading through the dense forest. The crowns of the old
trees leave the forest in an unreal twilight illumination. The path continues
east and west.

Rooms.Name: Edge of a Dense Forest
Rooms.Description: The dense forest surrounds you with towering trees that reach for the sky, their branches intermingling overhead to form a thick canopy that blocks out much of the sunlight and casts deep shadows below. The ground beneath your feet is soft and spongy, covered in a carpet of fallen leaves and pine needles. Ferns and other undergrowth flourish in abundance, dotted with wildflowers that add pops of color to the lush green landscape. The air is thick with the fragrant scent of pine and damp earth, and the rustling of leaves and the chirping of insects fills the air with a tranquil hum.

The air is thick with the fragrant scent of pine and damp earth, and the rustling of leaves and the chirping of insects fills the air with a tranquil hum.

Rooms.Description: The dense forest surrounds you with towering trees that reach for the sky, their branches intermingling overhead to form a thick canopy that blocks out much of the sunlight and casts deep shadows below. Rooms.Name: Tigris River
Rooms.Description:
Still wide enough for boats to pass, yet the banks of the river are covered
in tall grass and ferns, blocking your view beyond. Various trees and shrubs
can also be seen, providing shade and food for a multitude of animals.

Rooms.Name: Inside A Massive Living Tree
Rooms.Description:
You are in a legendary guild of rangers and woodsmen inside this massive
living tree. The tree is said to be centuries old, with roots that spread
far and wide, and a trunk so thick that it would take several people
holding hands to encircle it. Within its walls, the guild members live and
train, honing their skills in tracking, and survival. The interior of the
tree is lit by glowing mushrooms and torches, and the air is filled with
the scent of wood and earth.

Rooms.Name: Deep Within the Massive Living Tree
Rooms.Description:
Deep within the heart of the giant living tree, there is a small, cozy room
where the guildmaster awaits his students. The room is adorned with
intricate wooden carvings and tapestries depicting woodland scenes, and the
walls are lined with shelves holding various weapons, scrolls, and books. A
large wooden desk sits in the center of the room, and behind it sits the
guildmaster's chair, carved from a single piece of oak. The room is lit by
flickering candles, giving it a warm and inviting glow. This is where the
guildmaster interviews and advances his students, imparting his knowledge
and wisdom upon them as they progress through the ranks of the guild. The
air in the room is heavy with the scent of parchment and ink, and the sound
of rustling leaves can be heard faintly in the background, reminding all
who enter of the forest's presence.

Mobiles.LongDescription: John the Lumberjack is here, looking for some trees to chop down.
Mobiles.Description:
He is six feet tall and looks quite strong, muscles bulging under his heavy,
chequered shirt.  His features are worn with hard work and his expression is
one of a peaceful man leading a simple life.

Mobiles.LongDescription: A big, brown, angry-looking bear is here.
Mobiles.Description:
The bear is a big, brown, furry animal with very large claws and very sharp
teeth.  It doesn't resemble those cute little thingies from toy shops at all.

Mobiles.LongDescription: A ferocious rabbit is here, glaring hungrily at you.
Mobiles.Description:
This small, furry creature with long ears and big feet has been attacked by
the dreaded rabbit rabies, a horrible disease that turns helpless and innocent
rabbits into ferocious and bloodthirsty monsters.

Mobiles.LongDescription: A fallow deer is grazing peacefully here.
Mobiles.Description:
She is a graceful creature on long, slender legs, and with large, brown eyes
looking back at you with an air of watchful interest.

Mobiles.LongDescription: A brown fox is here, looking for some rabbits to chew up.
Mobiles.Description: It is a large fox with beautiful, red-brown fur and a long, thick brush.

Mobiles.LongDescription: A vicious warg is here, snarling angrily at you.
Mobiles.Description:
It is an exceptionally large wolf with thick, black fur.  Saliva is dripping
quickly from its long, white fangs.  It looks quite dangerous and very angry.

Mobiles.LongDescription: A ferocious warg is here, snarling angrily at you.
Mobiles.Description:
It is an exceptionally large wolf with thick, black fur.  Saliva is dripping
quickly from its long, white fangs.  It looks quite dangerous and very angry.

Mobiles.LongDescription: A large, grey wolf is here, glaring hungrily at you.
Mobiles.Description: The large, grey wolf eyes you with interest while licking its lips.

Mobiles.LongDescription: A large, black wolf is here, glaring hungrily at you.
Mobiles.Description: The large, black wolf eyes you with interest while licking its lips.

Mobiles.LongDescription: A huge green dragon is here, its narrow yellow eyes glowing with rage.
Mobiles.Description:
This enormous winged serpent has dark green scales covering most of its
colossal body.  Numerous holes in its heavy wings tell of many fights as does
the nicks in the horns on its head.  It smells as disgusting as only dragons
do.

Mobiles.LongDescription: Shargugh the Forest Brownie is here, grinning broadly at you.
Mobiles.Description:
This little fellow is only three foot tall with wild matted brown hair and long
tangled brown beard.  He wears ragged brown and green clothing and looks as if
he is having great fun.

Mobiles.LongDescription: The elder druid is here ... he looks very upset at your presence in his home.
Mobiles.Description:
The druid looks quite old.  You would think him venerable, but you know
he would be a tough foe.

Mobiles.LongDescription: A bunny rabbit hops around playfully.
Mobiles.Description:
This rabbit is a small, furry animal with long hind legs and short front legs.
It has a round, compact body and a short, fluffy tail. It has large, round ears
that can move independently, and its eyes are situated on the sides of its head,
giving it a wide field of vision. Its fur is soft and gray. It has large, strong
hind legs that it uses for jumping and running, and sharp claws that it uses for
digging burrows. It has large, flat teeth designed for chewing tough vegetation.
Overall, this rabbit have a distinctive and recognizable appearance, with its
soft, round body and long hind legs making it look both cute and nimble.

Mobiles.LongDescription: Thalionorin Leafwhisperer, master of the rangers guild rests here waiting for the next student.
Mobiles.Description:
A tall, lean, and muscular figure with piercing green eyes, long curly brown
hair, and dons a suit of green and brown leather armor. Thalionorin is a skilled
master ranger, holding a staff made from the wood of this massive. He is wise
and compassionate, with a deep love for nature and its balance. As guildmaster,
Thalionorin trains and mentors new rangers while overseeing guild operations
with a fair but firm leadership style, earning the respect and reverence of all
who know him.

Mobiles.LongDescription:
The ranger guild guard is alert here, scanning the shadows and bushes for
someone trying to sneak into the guild.
Mobiles.Description:
Dressed in green and brown leather armor adorned with nature-inspired designs,
this ranger guard blends in seamlessly with the surrounding forest. The ranger
is peaceful sort, preferring to use non-lethal means to subdue intruders
whenever possible, using deadly force only as a last resort to protect the
living tree and its guild members.
